# datafeta-infra — VPS infrastructure for datafeta.io
#
# Repos:
#   app:     https://github.com/henrywiechert/data-slicer
#   website: https://github.com/henrywiechert/datafeta-website
#   infra:   https://github.com/henrywiechert/datafeta-infra  (this repo)
#
# VPS layout:
#   /opt/datafeta-infra/        ← this repo, cloned on the VPS
#   /opt/datafeta-data/
#     snapshots/                ← persistent DataSlicer snapshot storage
#
# Host services: Nginx (TLS termination + reverse proxy), certbot (Let's Encrypt)
# Containers:    app (port 8100), website (port 8101)
#                All ports bound to 127.0.0.1 — Nginx proxies externally.
#
# First-time setup: see scripts/setup-vps.sh
# Deploy app:       scripts/deploy-app.sh [TAG]
# Deploy website:   scripts/deploy-website.sh [TAG]
